<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Coming Soon</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">

    <style>
        body {
            background: #06060a;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden;
            font-family: "Pretendard", sans-serif;
        }

        .coming-wrapper {
            text-align: center;
            animation: fadeIn 1.4s ease;
        }

        .loader {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border: 6px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border-top-color: #ffffffcc;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            to {
                transform: rotate(360deg);
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        a.back {
            margin-top: 35px;
            display: inline-block;
            color: #ccc;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-decoration: underline;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        a.back:hover {
            opacity: 1;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="coming-wrapper">
        <div class="loader"></div>
        <h2>아직 준비중입니다</h2>
        <p>서비스가 완성되면 바로 업데이트해드릴게요.</p>
        <a href="/" class="back">← 포트폴리오로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
</body>

</html>